  Read of size 8 at addr c0000000023e7a90 by task swapper/0

  CPU: 0 PID: 0 Comm: swapper Not tainted 5.2.0-rc2-next-20190528-02824-g048a6ab4835b #113
  Call Trace:
    dump_stack+0x104/0x154 (unreliable)
